{"type":"message","id":"a54d49ac","parentId":"c38fbd66","timestamp":"2026-07-13T03:18:47.933Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-07-13 11:18:47 GMT+8] Exec completed (nova-ced, code 0) :: ADHD_agent\\media-crawler-mcp\\cache\\local_cache.py:112>> 2026-07-13 11:18:46 asyncio ERROR (base_events.py:1875) - Task was destroyed but it is pending! task: <Task cancelling name…\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/linkang/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Monday, July 13th, 2026 — 11:18 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-07-13 03:18 UTC"}],"timestamp":1783912727931}}
